    "name": "Tuxedo (2)",
    "profile": "Hailing from historical city of Gdansk, polish dj and producer Tuxedo is a part of club scene for more than a decade. His devotion and exceptional taste for various electronic music flavours were quickly noticed and led him to perform in many respected venues and later on becoming a resident dj in oldest polish club Sfinks700. Shared the stage with Sven Vath, Adriatique, Sasha & Digweed, Booka Shade and many other greats. He's also a founder of Electronic Tree imprint and one half of Fluente duo along his studio partner Monojoke. Constantly on a mission exploring deeper sides of house music.",
